      "text": "We went out to the bathroom and washed up and walked a little bit at night.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And during the day, we stayed inside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We couldn't see any daylight for a year and a half, practically.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Entire time, we didn't see any daylight at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had to, uh, sit there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
